ystem integration (Calendar, Maps, Search) and expects a seamless transition between her Macbook and iPhone.", "tech": {"internet": 5, "gadgets": 5}, "brands": ["Apple", "Starbucks", "Zomato"], "needs": ["Zero-click results (Snippets)", "Cross-device synchronization", "Advanced search filters"], "frustrations": ["Ad-heavy top results", "Privacy concerns regarding tracking", "Autocomplete errors for local slang"], "photo_url": "file:///Users/ni3_kr/Documents/UX/CaseStudyBuilder/static/img/personas/international/global_female_2.png"}]}, {"type": "competitive", "label": "Research", "title": "Competitive Analysis", "data": [{"competitor": "Microsoft Bing", "pros": ["Better rewards program (Microsoft Rewards)", "Stronger integration with Windows ecosystem"], "cons": ["Slower indexing of local Indian content", "Interface feels cluttered compared to Google"]}, {"competitor": "DuckDuckGo", "pros": ["High privacy standards/No tracking", "Clean, non-intrusive interface"], "cons": ["Lacks hyper-local Indian context", "Voice search is significantly less accurate"]}]}, {"type": "journey_map", "label": "Synthesize", "title": "User Journey Map", "stages": [{"stage": "AWARENESS", "touchpoints": "Mobile Browser, App Icon", "actions": "User feels a need to know something and opens the browser.", "emotions": "curious and focused", "ownership": "Marketing & OS Integration"}, {"stage": "CONSIDERATION", "touchpoints": "Search Bar, Voice Icon, Lens Icon", "actions": "User decides whether to type, speak, or use an image to search.", "emotions": "determined but impatient", "ownership": "Core Search UI"}, {"stage": "DECISION", "touchpoints": "SERP (Search Engine Results Page)", "actions": "User scans titles and snippets to find the most credible source.", "emotions": "evaluative and cautious", "ownership": "Ranking & AI Teams"}, {"stage": "SERVICE", "touchpoints": "Third-party Website, Knowledge Graph", "actions": "User consumes the information or clicks through to a site.", "emotions": "satisfied or frustrated by speed", "ownership": "Infrastructure/Partners"}, {"stage": "LOYALTY", "touchpoints": "Discover Feed, History Tab", "actions": "User returns for related queries or follows a topic.", "emotions": "trusting and reliant", "ownership": "Retention/Growth"}]}, {"type": "wireframes", "label": "Ideation", "title": "Structural Wireframes", "screens": [{"title": "Option A: Minimalist India Search", "platform": "web", "layout": [{"type": "header", "content": {"logo_text": "Google India", "nav": ["Images", "Gmail", "Account"]}}, {"type": "hero", "content": {"headline": "Search the world's information", "subheadline": "Now available in 9 Indian languages", "cta": "Google Search"}}, {"type": "feature_grid", "content": [{"title": "Voice Search", "desc": "Speak in your native tongue."}, {"title": "Google Lens", "desc": "Search what you see."}]}, {"type": "cta_banner", "content": {"headline": "Switch to Hindi, Bangla, or Telugu", "cta": "Change Language"}}, {"type": "footer", "content": {"copyright": "\u00a9 2024 Google - India"}}]}, {"title": "Option B: Discovery-Led Search", "platform": "web", "layout": [{"type": "header", "content": {"logo_text": "Google", "nav": ["Weather: 32\u00b0C", "IPL Scores"]}}, {"type": "hero", "content": {"headline": "What's happening today?", "subheadline": "Localized updates for your city.", "cta": "Search Now"}}, {"type": "feature_grid", "content": [{"title": "Top News", "desc": "Curated headlines for you."}, {"title": "Market Trends", "desc": "BSE/NSE updates real-time."}, {"title": "Jobs", "desc": "New openings near you."}]}, {"type": "cta_banner", "content": {"headline": "Personalize your feed", "cta": "Follow Topics"}}, {"type": "footer", "content": {"copyright": "Privacy | Terms | Advertising"}}]}]}, {"type": "ui_preview", "label": "Final Design", "title": "High-Fidelity Interface", "device_type": "macbook", "screenshot_url": "file:///Users/ni3_kr/Documents/UX/CaseStudyBuilder/static/output/ui_933fc74f-0207-47db-bede-556baf